OL,3,CCouncil refunds #485,000 for wrongly
OL,4,Cfining drivers in the bus lane
OL,6,FA London council is refunding almost
OL,7,Fhalf a million pounds in bus lane
OL,8,Ffines after quoting the wrong law on
OL,9,Ftickets.
OL,11,FSouthwark Council handed out more than
OL,12,F10,000 penalty charge notices in four
OL,13,Fmonths.
OL,15,FBut a Freedom of Information request
OL,16,Fexposed an error caused by the
OL,17,F"incorrect template copied over the
OL,18,Fbus lane template".
