OL,3,CCouncil refunds #485,000 for wrongly
OL,4,Cfining drivers in the bus lane
OL,6,FThe data request was submitted by
OL,7,FPhillip Morgan who was initially
OL,8,Fbrushed off by the council.
OL,10,F"When I told them about this in April,
OL,11,Fthey said to me, well, sorry, you're
OL,12,Fwrong. Go and have a nice day,"
OL,13,FPhillip told ITV News London.
OL,15,F"So I then threatened them with the
OL,16,FHigh Courts and now they've actually
OL,17,Fwoken up and realised their error.
OL,19,F"(The council) will pay back roughly
OL,20,F#485,000," he explained.
