OL,3,CCouncil refunds #485,000 for wrongly
OL,4,Cfining drivers in the bus lane
OL,6,FThe council blamed the mistake on a
OL,7,Fcontractor and said all fines would
OL,8,Fautomatically be paid back or
OL,9,Fcancelled, adding: "We are also
OL,10,Fstrengthening our check with
OL,11,Fcontractors to make sure this does not
OL,12,Fhappen again.
OL,14,F"The council will recover the full
OL,15,Fcost of the refunds from the
OL,16,Fcontractors."
OL,18,FPhillip has been fighting for
OL,19,Fmotorists for 15 year after
OL,20,Fsuccessfully challenging a ticket
OL,21,Fissued to his son.
